description: Try our easy to follow Cheese Bread recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Savoury muffin,Pescatarian,Seafood free,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Low sugar,Sesame free,Father's Day,Halal,Soy free,Wheat free,Vegetarian,Peanut free
name: Cheese Bread Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 200Â°C. Line a 12-hole muffin tin with baking paper.
Place milk and oil into a saucepan. Season with salt and pepper. Place over medium heat. Cook for 4 minutes or until mixture just comes to the boil.

Transfer to a food processor. Add rice flour, baking powder and egg. Process until well combined. Grate parmesan and 120g tasty cheese. Set 2 tbs parmesan aside. Add remaining grated cheese to the food processor and process until just combined.

Spoon mixture into prepared tins. Cut remaining tasty cheese into small squares. Press a square into each bread and sprinkle with reserved parmesan. Bake for 20 minutes or until puffed and golden. Serve warm.
